### List all matches
GET http://localhost:8080/api/matches
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get match by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/matches/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create new match
POST http://localhost:8080/api/matches
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "team1Id": 1,
    "team2Id": 2,
    "date": "2024-04-25T10:00:00Z",
    "location": "Stadium A",
    "score1": 0,
    "score2": 0
}

### Update match
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/matches/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "team1Id": 1,
    "team2Id": 2,
    "date": "2024-04-25T10:00:00Z",
    "location": "Stadium B",
    "score1": 2,
    "score2": 1
}

### Delete match
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/matches/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update match players
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/matches/1/players
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "team1Players": [1, 2, 3],
    "team2Players": [4, 5, 6]
}

### Get match statistics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/matches/1/statistics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}} 